    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Note: ||= does not exist. (logical or)\nYou can use </p>\n\n<pre><code>y= y || expr; // expr is NOT evaluated if y==true\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>y = expr ? true : y;  // expr is always evaluated.\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
